Hi guys!
Just wanted to fill in on what mixnic said earlier.

The game itself is faulty at the moment and there are several paying customers who cannot play the game either because it crashes during startup.
And if the game won't work itself it's probably very difficult, if not even impossible, to crack the game at the moment.

So until there is a patch released (~1 week), I advice you to just be patient and stop blaming the guys who spend loads of time without pay trying to bring the game to you for free. If you cannot do that, buy the game, but be warned that it might not even work for you then.
Cheers!
